{"video_id": "0VdamPvV1No", "title": "Real Renunciation | HG Amitasana Dasa", "speaker": "HG Amitasana Dasa", "youtube_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0VdamPvV1No", "duration": 218, "segments": [{"start": 0.0, "end": 4.0, "text": " What is Real Renunciation and What is False Renunciation?"}, {"start": 9.0, "end": 15.0, "text": " That's why Rupa Goswami says, what is real renunciation and what is false renunciation."}, {"start": 15.0, "end": 27.0, "text": " When one gives up objects thinking that they are material without seeing connection with the Lord,"}, {"start": 27.0, "end": 31.0, "text": " that renunciation is false renunciation."}, {"start": 36.0, "end": 46.0, "text": " That Vastu, that thing, if that relationship with the Lord is not seen and one gives up that object,"}, {"start": 46.0, "end": 51.0, "text": " money, suppose somebody has money, this is Maya."}, {"start": 53.0, "end": 55.0, "text": " Money is Maya."}, {"start": 55.0, "end": 57.0, "text": " But does not see a relationship with the Lord."}, {"start": 57.0, "end": 59.0, "text": " Connection with the Lord."}, {"start": 62.0, "end": 66.0, "text": " Budhya means with that understanding, with that consciousness."}, {"start": 66.0, "end": 68.0, "text": " It is material."}, {"start": 68.0, "end": 71.0, "text": " It is of this material world."}, {"start": 73.0, "end": 75.0, "text": " There is Sambandha."}, {"start": 75.0, "end": 77.0, "text": " Money has Sambandha with the Lord or not?"}, {"start": 79.0, "end": 81.0, "text": " Lakshmi is a consort of Narayana."}, {"start": 81.0, "end": 84.0, "text": " But if we don't see that connection"}, {"start": 84.0, "end": 85.0, "text": " and"}, {"start": 86.0, "end": 88.0, "text": " we want to enjoy that Lakshmi,"}, {"start": 88.0, "end": 90.0, "text": " that is material."}, {"start": 92.0, "end": 95.0, "text": " Ravana wanted to enjoy Sita."}, {"start": 95.0, "end": 97.0, "text": " He is called Ravana."}, {"start": 98.0, "end": 99.0, "text": " A demon."}, {"start": 99.0, "end": 102.0, "text": " We burn the effigy and we celebrate that."}, {"start": 104.0, "end": 108.0, "text": " When Ram wants to enjoy Sita, nothing wrong about it."}, {"start": 109.0, "end": 111.0, "text": " Hanuman is also wanting Sita, yes or no?"}, {"start": 111.0, "end": 114.0, "text": " He went all the way to Lanka to get Sita."}, {"start": 115.0, "end": 119.0, "text": " But for Ravana."}, {"start": 119.0, "end": 122.0, "text": " You see, both are after Sita."}, {"start": 122.0, "end": 124.0, "text": " Ravana is also after Sita."}, {"start": 124.0, "end": 125.0, "text": " Hanuman is also after Sita."}, {"start": 125.0, "end": 127.0, "text": " Both want Sita."}, {"start": 127.0, "end": 130.0, "text": " But Ravana wants Sita for himself."}, {"start": 130.0, "end": 134.0, "text": " Hanuman wants Sita so that he can take it and give it to Ravana."}, {"start": 134.0, "end": 135.0, "text": " Both are wanting Sita."}, {"start": 135.0, "end": 139.0, "text": " Now both of us can be, all of us can be wanting money."}, {"start": 139.0, "end": 144.0, "text": " We can be gunning after more money."}, {"start": 144.0, "end": 148.0, "text": " To earn more money."}, {"start": 148.0, "end": 150.0, "text": " Want to have more money."}, {"start": 150.0, "end": 152.0, "text": " Is it Maya? Yes or no?"}, {"start": 152.0, "end": 156.0, "text": " If one thinks money is Maya, I don't want money."}, {"start": 156.0, "end": 158.0, "text": " Or gives up all this."}, {"start": 158.0, "end": 160.0, "text": " This house is Maya."}, {"start": 160.0, "end": 162.0, "text": " That is Falcovaira."}, {"start": 162.0, "end": 164.0, "text": " Hari Sambandha Vastuna."}, {"start": 164.0, "end": 166.0, "text": " There is Hari Sambandha."}, {"start": 166.0, "end": 168.0, "text": " To use it in the service of the Lord,"}, {"start": 168.0, "end": 170.0, "text": " thinking that it belongs to the Lord,"}, {"start": 170.0, "end": 172.0, "text": " it is energy of the Lord,"}, {"start": 172.0, "end": 176.0, "text": " that spiritualizes that thing."}, {"start": 176.0, "end": 179.0, "text": " Yukta Vairagya Ucyate."}, {"start": 179.0, "end": 183.0, "text": " That is Yukta Vairagya."}, {"start": 183.0, "end": 185.0, "text": " A devotee of the Lord,"}, {"start": 185.0, "end": 188.0, "text": " not only the things he has in this body,"}, {"start": 188.0, "end": 191.0, "text": " is whose energy?"}, {"start": 191.0, "end": 194.0, "text": " The Lord's energy."}, {"start": 194.0, "end": 196.0, "text": " Given by the Lord."}, {"start": 196.0, "end": 200.0, "text": " This intelligence, this mind, this ability, this talent,"}, {"start": 200.0, "end": 202.0, "text": " is given by the Lord."}, {"start": 202.0, "end": 205.0, "text": " Use it in the service of the Lord."}, {"start": 205.0, "end": 209.0, "text": " And that spiritualizes the existence."}]}